flowchart TD
    Start([App launch]) --> BtPerms{Bluetooth permissions granted?}
    BtPerms -->|No| RequestBt[Request BLUETOOTH_SCAN and BLUETOOTH_CONNECT]
    BtPerms -->|Yes| CheckUsbPermission[Request USB permission for Zebra VID 1504 if device is present]
    RequestBt --> BtGrant{Both granted?}
    BtGrant -->|No| StopInit[Stop RFID init]
    BtGrant -->|Yes| CheckUsbPermission

    CheckUsbPermission --> InitSdk[InitRfidSDK]
    InitSdk --> UsbReaders[Build Readers with SERVICE_USB]
    UsbReaders --> UsbFound{USB readers available?}
    UsbFound -->|Yes| SelectUsb[Prefer readerName, else first USB reader]
    UsbFound -->|No or InvalidUsage| BtReaders[Dispose and rebuild Readers with BLUETOOTH]

    BtReaders --> BtFound{Bluetooth readers available?}
    BtFound -->|Yes| SelectBt[Prefer readerNamebt or readerNameRfd8500, else first BT reader]
    BtFound -->|No| NoReader[Show failure status]

    SelectUsb --> Connect[Connect selected reader]
    SelectBt --> Connect
    Connect --> ConnectOk{Connected?}
    ConnectOk -->|No| NoReader
    ConnectOk -->|Yes| Configure[Configure trigger, tag, disconnect, and inventory events]
    Configure --> Ready([Connected and ready])

    Ready --> Runtime{Runtime event}
    Runtime -->|USB attached| UsbAttach[Dismiss dialog and re-init SDK]
    Runtime -->|USB detached or BT disconnect| Recover[Destroy reader and show reconnect dialog]
    Runtime -->|Trigger| Inventory[Start or stop inventory]
    Runtime -->|Tag data| UpdateUi[Append tag data to UI]

    UsbAttach --> InitSdk
    Inventory --> Ready
    UpdateUi --> Ready

    Recover --> Choice{User choice}
    Choice -->|Connect Bluetooth| DelayBt[Schedule BT reconnect after 5 seconds]
    Choice -->|Wait for USB| WaitUsb[Wait for next USB attach broadcast]
    DelayBt --> InitSdk
    WaitUsb --> UsbAttach

    style Start fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#1976d2,stroke-width:2px
    style Ready fill:#c8e6c9,stroke:#388e3c,stroke-width:2px
    style StopInit fill:#ffcdd2,stroke:#d32f2f,stroke-width:2px
    style NoReader fill:#fff3cd,stroke:#ff9800,stroke-width:2px